*Prerequisites for Spin-1 Systems:*
- Normalization condition: $ sum bar.v c_m bar.v^2 = 1 $.
- Complex amplitudes: $ bar.v 2i bar.v^2 = (2i)(-2i) = 4 $.
- Expectation values: $ chevron.l S_z chevron.r = sum bar.v c_m bar.v^2 (m planck) $.
- Operator moments: $ chevron.l S_z^2 chevron.r = sum bar.v c_m bar.v^2 (m planck)^2 $.
